data.name: Label3.Text
data.value:
If you enable this feature, anonymous usage statistics data will be sent periodically to the developer, including, but no limited to:
- Country Region Code - Operating System Version - Session Duration Number of Sessions per Day - Name of the Property Packages added to the Flowsheet - Number of Compounds added to the Simulation - Type of Reactions added to the Flowsheet - Type of the Objects added to the Flowsheet - DWSIM Tools and Utilities used by you (i.e. Sensitivity Analysis Utility) - Time Taken to Solve the Flowsheet - Error (Exception) information
This data is completely anonymous and will be used to help the developers to focus on the features that are used the most. Error reports do not include any personal information and will be used by the developers to quickly identify and fix bugs, without the need for you to report this error on the Forums.
Additionally, if you enter your email below, you may be contacted by the developer if an error occurs during usage of DWSIM Simulator, in order to collect more information about the event and further accelerate the process of fixing the error.
For more information, please read the Privacy Policy.
Thank you for your help!
